<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_196_r1l22"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> wır tun eẅch ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ einr . genant v̈lein turner </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_196_r1l23">von <expan>Mülſtett<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu Swabach ʒu fenknuſſ . komen ıſt . der hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_196_r1l24">vnbetwungenlıch bekant vnd geſagt etlıch ſtuk vnd artıkel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_196_r1l25">Vnd wan vns dunkt daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">eẅch </del> des ein notdurft ſey daʒ Jr das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_196_r1l26">wıſſet . ſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> bekentnuſſ . ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_196_r1l27">abſchrıft <expan>hıerinn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> . daʒ Jr eẅch darnach wıſſet ʒu <expan>rıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_196_r1l28">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> . lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_196" id="98r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat zu <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> wir tun ewch zu
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz einr genant Ülein Turner von
                                <expan>Mülstett<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Swabach zu fenknuss komen ist,
                        der hat unbetwungenlich bekant und gesagt etlich stuk und artikel und, wan
                        uns dunkt, daz des ein notdurft sey, daz ir das wisset, so
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> bekentnuss ein abschrift
                                <expan>hierinn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>, daz ir ewch darnach wisset zu
                                <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
